^B@2^*BHoward Schutzman: ^*N|cp||at|Cohen recommends that opener can't reverse unless responder's first bid is at the 1-level. If you follow his recommendation, then|

ht|d|cs|6|at|^b{|ia|,1dp1sp!2h|at|}|ht|d|at|^L@22@H in this auction is a reverse, but |
