cs|6|fp|1|ht|b|at|^-{      Quick summary      }

|ht|e|cs|1|cp|4|at|{  Opener's Jumpshift = Game forcing
    (Roughly 18/19 or more up to a 2C Opening)    }

|ht|i|cs|5|cp|3|at|{  Opener's Reverse = One-round forcing
    (Roughly 16 or more up to a 2C Opening)    }
^-|fp||cs||cp||ht|l|at|^B@2

What happens after the reverse? You can just "wing it," if you wish, but next is a simple (and common) system:|
PG| ***** 44 ***** |


